Dick Wesson (announcer) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dick_Wesson_(announcer) 0 Dick Wesson (February 20, 1919 – January 27, 1979) was an American movie and television announcer. He is best known as the announcer for The Wonderful World of Disney from 1954–1979, and many Quinn Martin series.
